<p>Tatiana recently played Radiant Assembly of God Sister preacher Alice McKeegan in HBO detective drama Perry Mason, which was renewed for a second season on July 22.</p>

<p>Maslany gushed via Instagram on August 9: 'I love this show and loved playing the absolute creature that is Sister Alice.'</p>

<p>Erle Stanley Gardner created the reboot of the CBS series (1957-1966), which features Matthew Rhys, John Lithgow, Juliet Rylance, Chris Chalk, and Shea Whigham. </p>

